overview: 1998 K-State vs Nebraska: Special Director's Cut Edition The greatest game of the #1 Season is available on DVD for the first time ever, in this 2-disc Special Edition Wildcat Classic. Featuring: •Complete game replay (1st time on DVD!) •Optional audio track, with all new commentary from Coach Bill Snyder and former players Damion McIntosh and Jeremy Martin recorded this Summer •Pregame Hype (includes ESPN Gameday) •Postgame Locker room Celebration •1998 Season Highlights (1st time on DVD!)
title: K-State | Nebraska 1998
